      • getAssetDependencies

        public java.util.List<Reference> getAssetDependencies(java.lang.String asset,
                                             java.lang.String service)
        Retrieves asset option dependencies for the defined asset.

        API Call: GET /api/options/{asset}/dependencies?service={service}

        Parameters:
        asset - Name of the asset to retrieve dependencies for.
        service - The serviceId of the service descriptor or ID of the catalog service. The service is used to compute dependencies for a particular service form.
        Returns:
        Dependencies for this asset type.
